The Wyoming Cowboys represented the [[University of Wyoming]] in the [[1987 NCAA Division I-A football season]]. The Cowboys offense scored 426 points, while the defense allowed 271 points. At seasonâs end, the Cowboys appeared in the [[1987 Holiday Bowl]].
